{"tid":2317947,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國：共匪試圖展開軍備競賽 美軍必須做準備","createTime":"2020-12-09T03:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T05:46:20.000Z","uid":21470,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fdd6650ff9514f8de7c73db163bb2248a82ad97f","tid":2317947,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T03:27:39.000Z","msg":"美參聯主席：中國提升軍事能力　試圖2035年前追上美國 <br />\n<br />\n美國參謀長聯席會議主席米利表示，中國投放資源提升軍事能力，試圖在2035年追上美國，目標在本世紀中期於軍事衝突中打敗美國，中國在現時與未來都會為美國造成重大安全挑戰。米利出席《華爾街日報》行政總裁議會高峰會時表示，美方不希望大國間的競爭，演變成大國間的戰爭，憂慮會演變成災難。 <br />\n<br />\n米利說，中國40年前的軍力完全難以追上美國，但在經濟發展後，中方投資遠洋海軍、發展新式戰鬥機等，並往太空和網路軍事方面進發，日後必定會與美國平起平坐，<span class=\"gold\">美軍必須在太空與網路方面做好準備</span>，以面對中國和俄羅斯等對手。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2369895\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2369895&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W1BOXtrJgaeu%2B3uDm9UxZFo%3D&h=919dc211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2369895</a>"},{"pid":"c9d81e1a21c64b52c98b26e87c8a2881532b2234","tid":2317947,"uid":15358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T03:55:03.000Z","msg":"平起平坐？ 搞掂隻船唔噴黑煙先喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfcbb664221ba9d74696453b12c3fa894c07e71","tid":2317947,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"又想國會課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f7bf0acd8677f2fa8d612a9667ab28c8e3e37b","tid":2317947,"uid":71213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdfcbb664221ba9d74696453b12c3fa894c07e71","tid":2317947,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"又想國會課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"次次都係咁架啦 都係想要錢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=